  * fix #7118: fix bridge port detection when plugging netdev with vlan.

 -- Proxmox Support Team <support@proxmox.com>  Wed, 10 Dec 2025 20:26:23 +0100

libpve-common-perl (8.3.4) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * inotify/interfaces: use ip link for detecting physical interfaces and
    avoid restriction to only recognizing interfaces following a specific
    naming pattern.

  * interfaces: make parser aware of interface alternative names to avoid
    duplicate entries if the /e/n/i config used an altname while the parser
    still checked for only the primary one.

  * network: add 'if' prefix to the regex heuristic to detect physical network
    interfaces.

  * network: add 'nic' prefix to the regex heuristic to detect physical
    network interfaces.

  * network: add helpers to get`ip link` and `ip altname` information.

 -- Proxmox Support Team <support@proxmox.com>  Tue, 05 Aug 2025 16:29:17 +0200

